WEBVTT

00:00:01.079 --> 00:00:03.222
I love dumplings.

00:00:03.246 --> 00:00:06.936
But I seldom have dumplings
in a restaurant,

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:09.698
because my mom's cooking is the best.

00:00:10.476 --> 00:00:14.942
One day, I happened to take a bite
of Dumpling Xi's dish.

00:00:14.966 --> 00:00:16.316
To my surprise,

00:00:16.340 --> 00:00:18.734
they had a flavor of going home.

00:00:19.458 --> 00:00:22.979
Fresh, chewy and unexpected.

00:00:23.829 --> 00:00:25.948
In addition to being a dumpling lover,

00:00:25.972 --> 00:00:28.361
I actually have a full-time job.

00:00:28.385 --> 00:00:30.440
I am a management consultant,